<eesti>Saastetasu m&auml;&auml;rad saasteainete viimisel veekogudesse, p&otilde;hjavette v&otilde;i pinnasesse </eesti>
<inglise>Pollution charge rates for release of pollutants into water bodies, groundwater or soil </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Saastetasu m&auml;&auml;rad kroonides saasteaine tonni kohta j&auml;rgmiste saasteainete viimisel veekogudesse, p&otilde;hjavette v&otilde;i pinnasesse: </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The pollution charge rates in kroons per one ton of pollutant for the release of the following pollutants into water bodies, groundwater or soil are as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>1) orgaanilised ained, arvutatuna nende lagundamise biokeemilisele hapnikutarbele seitsme &ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva jooksul (BHT <hi rend="sub"> 7 </hi>) - alates 2002. aasta 1. jaanuarist 3252,0 krooni, alates 2003. aasta 1. jaanuarist 3902,0 krooni, alates 2004. aasta 1. jaanuarist 4683,0 krooni, alates 2005. aasta 1. jaanuarist 5619,0 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>1) organic matter, calculated as the biochemical oxygen demand for the decomposition of such matter during seven twenty-four hour periods (BOD <hi rend="sub"> 7 </hi>) - 3252.0 kroons as of 1 January 2002, 3902.0 kroons as of 1 January 2003, 4683.0 kroons as of 1 January 2004, 5619.0 kroons as of 1 January 2005; </inglise>
<eesti>2) fosfori&uuml;hendid, arvutatuna &uuml;ldfosforiks (P <hi rend="sub"> &uuml;ld </hi>) - alates 2002. aasta 1. jaanuarist 4898,0 krooni, alates 2003. aasta 1. jaanuarist 5878,0 krooni, alates 2004. aasta 1. jaanuarist 7054,0 krooni, alates 2005. aasta 1. jaanuarist 8464,0 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>2) phosphorous compounds, calculated as total phosphorus (P <hi rend="sub"> tot </hi>) - 4898.0 kroons as of 1 January 2002, 5878.0 kroons as of 1 January 2003, 7054.0 kroons as of 1 January 2004, 8464.0 kroons as of 1 January 2005; </inglise>
<eesti>3) l&auml;mmastiku&uuml;hendid, arvutatuna &uuml;ldl&auml;mmastikuks (N <hi rend="sub"> &uuml;ld </hi>) - alates 2002. aasta 1. jaanuarist 3068,0 krooni, alates 2003. aasta 1. jaanuarist 3682,0 krooni, alates 2004. aasta 1. jaanuarist 4418,0 krooni, alates 2005. aasta 1. jaanuarist 5302,0 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>3) nitrogen compounds, calculated as total nitrogen (N <hi rend="sub"> tot </hi>) - 3068.0 kroons as of 1 January 2002, 3682.0 kroons as of 1 January 2003, 4418.0 kroons as of 1 January 2004, 5302.0 kroons as of 1 January 2005; </inglise>
<eesti>4) h&otilde;ljuvained - alates 2002. aasta 1. jaanuarist 1644,0 krooni, alates 2003. aasta 1. jaanuarist 1973,0 krooni, alates 2004. aasta 1. jaanuarist 2367,0 krooni, alates 2005. aasta 1. jaanuarist 2841,0 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>4) suspended solids - 1644.0 kroons as of 1 January 2002, 1973.0 kroons as of 1 January 2003, 2367.0 kroons as of 1 January 2004, 2841.0 kroons as of 1 January 2005; </inglise>
<eesti>5) sulfaadid, arvutatuna sulfaatiooniks (SO <hi rend="sub"> 4 </hi> <hi rend="sup"> 2- </hi>) - alates 2002. aasta 1. jaanuarist 33,0 krooni, alates 2003. aasta 1. jaanuarist 34,0 krooni, alates 2004. aasta 1. jaanuarist 38,0 krooni, alates 2005. aasta 1. jaanuarist 40,0 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>5) sulphates, calculated as sulphate ions (SO <hi rend="sub"> 4 </hi> <hi rend="sup"> 2- </hi>) - 33.0 kroons as of 1 January 2002, 34.0 kroons as of 1 January 2003, 38.0 kroons as of 1 January 2004, 40.0 kroons as of 1 January 2005; </inglise>
<eesti>6) &uuml;healuselised fenoolid - alates 2002. aasta 1. jaanuarist 21 810,0 krooni, alates 2003. aasta 1. jaanuarist 26 172,0 krooni, alates 2004. aasta 1. jaanuarist 31 406,0 krooni, alates 2005. aasta 1. jaanuarist 37 688,0 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>6) monophenols - 21 810.0 kroons as of 1 January 2002, 26 172.0 kroons as of 1 January 2003, 31 406.0 kroons as of 1 January 2004, 37 688.0 kroons as of 1 January 2005; </inglise>
<eesti>7) nafta, naftasaadused, mineraal&otilde;li ning tahke k&uuml;tuse ja muu orgaanilise aine termilise t&ouml;&ouml;tlemise vedelproduktid - alates 2002. aasta 1. jaanuarist 5192,0 krooni, alates 2003. aasta 1. jaanuarist 6231,0 krooni, alates 2004. aasta 1. jaanuarist 7477,0 krooni, alates 2005. aasta 1. jaanuarist 8972,0 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>7) oil, oil products, mineral oil or liquid products obtained from the thermal treatment of solid fuel or other organic matter - 5192.0 kroons as of 1 January 2002, 6231.0 kroons as of 1 January 2003, 7477.0 kroons as of 1 January 2004, 8972.0 kroons as of 1 January 2005. </inglise>
